Excellent! This is a cooking school fashioned as a urban restaurant.  All the food is made fresh on the premises.  The Cucumber Lemonade needs no sugar.  It is perfect as is. I have already invited friends to join me on a special group outing to eat here.  The price is surprisingly affordable.  What a special treat to have a quality eatery in the Brownsville community.  Yes, I would conduct tiny meetings here.  Yes,  it is spacious and transparent.  Yes, the sever is experienced with customer quality assurance.  Yes, highly visible from the street.
